summary: I’m just thinking about how tumblr was during the speak now era like it was wild and I miss it but I was such a shy bean who...
body: I’m just thinking about how tumblr was during the speak now era like it was wild and I miss it but I was such a shy bean who didn’t talk to anyone cos stranger danger lol. me and my best friends used to go on tumblr in our study break at school and send each other messages and pictures of Taylor!!! And we would follow along with the speak now concerts and lol I remember when Taylor had Justin as a special guest that was wild and when she had Selena we cried. Omg and the red era wow that was something else especially when I knew you were trouble was released and everyone had a melt down.
